# Lines below remap commit-author and commit-trailer identities so that
# `git shortlog -sne` and the GitHub contributors graph show a single
# canonical entry per person.
#
# Format reference: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitmailmap

# Fold `sumit-disseqt` (GitHub web-edit identity) into Sumit's main identity.
